      <title>彭博法国民意调查：勒庞的极右翼势力略有上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/france-elections-2024-le-pen-leads-in-bloomberg-poll-of-polls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的民意调查显示，在距离法国提前立法选举首轮投票仅剩九天之际，玛丽娜·勒庞领导的极右翼国民联盟的领先优势略有扩大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/france-elections-2024-le-pen-leads-in-bloomberg-poll-of-polls</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 10:25:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
